ta-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qig1665702804715.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qig1665702804715.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qig1665702804715.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qig1665702804715\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Define Properties\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Define the properties of the signature.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qig1665702804715__section_w50ab1b7b1_w51ab1b7_w52ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qig1665702804715__section_t3r_pmf_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1161307e60\">Fields</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"qig1665702804715__ul_zk1_qmf_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mak1665702804857.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mak1665702804857.html\" title=\"Determines whether the use of transactions is enabled for the component when run in a distributed transaction processing environment. Valid values are True or False (default).\">Use Transactions</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dqc1665702804994.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dqc1665702804994.html\" title=\"Defines whether the component is stateless.\">Component is Stateless</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hej1665702805069.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hej1665702805069.html\" title=\"Specifies how a transaction is ended if the component instance that started the transaction is deleted. The default action is rollback. If you select this property, a commit action is performed.\">Automatic Commit</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"okv1665702805139.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/okv1665702805139.html\" title=\"Implementation types for which call-in is available.\">Call-in Properties</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qig1665702804715__section_anc_smf_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1161307e117\">How to</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qig1665702804715__p_d6380e1_d6381e1_d6382e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zzx1665702678830.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zzx1665702678830.html\" title=\"Use the Signature Editor to create or modify component signatures. Signatures of Uniface components are automatically generated during compilation. Signatures of non-Uniface components can be created or imported.\">Define a Component Signature</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8421938\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8421938\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=